sub_title: Capital Lead at Techleap | Angel Investing | Strengthening the European startup ecosystem  | Regenerative society
summary:
Passionate about building a unified (early-stage)  innovation system for Europe, so countries and its citizens can truly start working together and remain competitive with other continents. 

Capital Lead at TechLeap (driver/lobby organisation of the Dutch tech sector). Network builder at ROM Utrecht (investor/booster of the NL economy in this region).

Founder of Fundsup, a platform that connects European tech ecosystems and its startups with relevant smart capital, making startup investing easy and accessible. 

Founder of Capital On Stage, a global VC event series that connects local founders with (international) VCs, politicians, and corporate leaders. 30+ hubs in Europe, Asia, and USA.
